page.title: 09People who have moved here.
page.content: {Mr. Reynolds}moved here because he has some holiday flats in Sutton on Sea. Before he came he lived in Nottinghamshire for 10 years. He has been in Sutton for 6 weeks.The village that{Mr. Reynolds}used to live in didn't have any shops. His hobbies is steam engines and vintage cars.One of {Mr. Reynold's}houses was near a river called the Trent and the other was near the Chesterfield Canal. The thing he likes about Sutton is the sea. The part he doesn't like is the winter. He will live here for most of his life. Where he used to live he had to go 7 miles to the shops but here he only has to go out of his front door.
